IF..ELIF..ELSE

$ cat test.py 
#!/usr/bin/python

ui=int(input("Enter any integer no: "))
if ui==0:print("Neither even nor odd...")
elif ui%2==0:print("Even No")
else:print("Odd No")

Executions:

$ ./test.py 
Enter any integer no: 10
Even No

$ ./test.py 
Enter any integer no: 13
Odd No

$ ./test.py 
Enter any integer no: 0
Neither even nor odd...

